    <p>The SUN Civil Society Network engages in advocacy at all levels, from lobbying local and national governments to influencing regional bodies and global forums.  Through our Advocacy working group we coordinate advocacy across the network to ensure our calls are amplified.</p>
    <p>Read more about some of our advocacy work below: </p>
